attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection
Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Welcome to 115 W. Third Street, an impeccably cared for detached, single-family in the heart of South Boston. Built in 2004, this 3-story home spans 2,700 sq ft of living space, offering a rare combination of timeless design, modern amenities, and unparalleled outdoor living. Boasting 3 beds, 2.5 baths, 2 fireplaces, and a wealth of outdoor retreats including a beautifully landscaped patio, 2 decks, and a rooftop deck. Entertain with ease in the open-concept first floor, featuring a spacious living room with fireplace, a chef's kitchen equipped with JennAir appliances, and a dining room with sliders to the gorgeous patio. The second floor boasts a second living area, and a peaceful primary suite complete with a cozy fireplace, walk-in closet, and spacious deck. The sun-filled third floor provides an additional bonus room with sky lights, two large bedrooms, and full bath. Nestled in a vibrant community, just blocks from the Broadway T Station, dining favorites, local shops and cafes.
